    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.8.8" />
                
                <fw type="curatorial">8</fw>
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                    <hi rend="caps">LELAND STANFORD JUNIOR UNIVERSITY
                    
                    DEPARTMENT OF ENGLISH
                    COMPARATIVE LITERATURE</hi>
                
                    <hi rend="italic">Stanford University, California,</hi>
                </fw>
                <opener>
                    <dateline>June 21, 1921</dateline>
                    
                    <salute>Dear Mr. Neihardt:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>My poetic anthology, called <title>"Poems of the English Race,"</title> for which you were good enough to let me have a selction from "The Song of Hugh Glass," has just appeared after some two years' delay; and I have asked the publishers to send you a copy, with my compliments. You may perhaps be interested in the special combination I have sought to make of British and American, classic and contemporary, verse; and if you should feel like expressing your opinion of the book to the publishers, they would be very grateful, as would I. Of course I should not suggest this if it were a matter of my own composition; but there need be no delicacy about mere editorship.</p>
                
                <p>I was pleased to have some word from your agent that you are expecting to be out this way again next fall or winter, and at once asked our Lecture Committee to try to plan for another visit to Stanford. We remember your former stay here with much pleasure.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Cordially yours,</salute>
                    
                    <signed>Raymond M. Alden</signed>
                
                    <address><addrLine>Mr. John <hi rend="caps">G.</hi> Neihardt</addrLine></address>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
